snippet.title: Contract Killer Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Contract Killer is a 2.5D co-op beat ‘em up starring a diverse cast of angry writing utensils. Punch, snap, and clap your way through baddies and bosses in a comical campaign, clash against your friends, or survive endless swarms of corporate goons!

OUT NOW on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1588250/Contract_Killer/

Join the Discord: bit.ly/3xAapdf
